sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant E as OpenCASE Editor
    participant K as Keycloak
    participant A as Auth0

    B->>E: Open Editor
    E->>K: Redirect to login page
    K->>K: Show "Login with Auth0"
    K->>A: Redirect to Auth0 login
    A->>A: User authenticates
    A->>K: Return auth code
    K->>K: Exchange code for tokens
    K->>K: Create/update local user
    K->>E: Return OIDC tokens
    E->>B: User is logged in
